About this item

  • All-Day Kids Fitness Tracker : Track your child's daily steps, calories burned, and distance walked. To keep the motivation high, kids earn virtual medals when they reach specific activity goals, making fitness fun and engaging.
  • 20+ Sport Modes & IP67 Waterproof: From running to basketball, soccer to cycling, our kids sports watch Tracker supports over 20+ different sports modes. Waterproof Activity Tracker, It can be used in water depth when washing hands and within 5 meters, but not bathing or swimming use , the kids tracker watch is built to keep up with their active lifestyle.
  • Sleep Tracker & Vibration Alarm Clockkids watch the sleep tracker can automatically track kids' sleep quality , including deep, light sleep, and awake. The vibration alarm clock ensures gentle waking without disturbing others, helping children develop regular sleep habits. Additionally, smart watch for boys girls also have water and sedentary vibration reminders
  • Kids Smart Watch Boys gift : Packaged beautifully, the kids fitness watch makes an ideal gift for birthdays, Christmas, or any special occasion. Paired with CO-FIT App, you can explore additional features and access detailed activity and health reports, making it a fantastic tool for kids .
  • Compatibility & Battery: kids watch boys Compatible with smartphones running iOS 11.0 and above or Android 5.0 and above. Please scan the QR code to download the CO-FIT APP and connect to the smart watch after downloading.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

    • Pedro R.
      5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality
      Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2025
      Color: BlackAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
      Good looking, good quality watch. Got this for my 8 years old and he's loving it.

      He's into tracking his workout routines, therefore this is perfect for him as he can keep track of his runs and general activity while playing / training. He tries to break his daily steps record every day.

      He monitors his hearth rate while working out and practices the watch breathing exercises to try to keep it under control. Funny how little kids these days have a natural ability to navigate through technology. He's been finding out on his own how to operate the different watch features.

      The watch does not have a camera, he was not impressed by that, however the features and screen quality are better than the regular kid watches and more comparable to a typical adult smart watch.

      My kid doesn't have a phone but you can take and make calls if you connect it to one. I set it up from my phone so I can do updates and change watch faces. It has a cool feature where you select a theme, and the app generates an AI picture for your background that you can personalize with your preferred shortcuts.

      Overall I think this watch is good value for money.

    • Daniel Moore
      5.0 out of 5 stars Great value and good functionality
      Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2024
      Color: BlackAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
      My 12 year old daughter is wearing her watch all day every day and only takes it off to charge it when she gets a shower. The watch has actually gotten her motivated to get up and move more. She's always making sure she reaches her step goals. I used to have difficulty getting her to exercise, but the watch has been the motivation that I was unable to provide any other way. That makes me really like this watch. Plus, since she wears it while sleeping, I know when she tries to stay up too late. It's gotten her to start actually going to bed on time, because now she knows I can track it. I told her if she takes it off while she sleeps, I'll assume she stayed up late and she'll be in trouble. Now she goes to bed at bedtime! I love it! That by itself makes it worth the investment to me!

      All the functionality works as advertised, and she's had fun making her own watch faces.

      Battery life seems to be quite good. She's gotten down to 75 percent in a single day, but that was the first day where she was constantly playing with changing watch faces and learning all the different functions. She puts it on the charger each day while in the shower, and it's fully charged when she gets out.

      This is definitely one I'd recommend. It's not something that gives a child too much screen time just by having it.

    • LEON
      5.0 out of 5 stars Nice affordable watch
      Reviewed in Canada on September 15, 2024
      Verified Purchase
      I got this kids' smart watch as a more affordable alternative to an Apple Watch, and honestly, its been great so far! It connects easily to iOS phones, and it even looks pretty similar, which makes it feel like a solid, budget-friendly option at this stage. I wasn't ready to risk giving my child an Apple Watch just yet, so this has been a perfect stand-in.

      One of the coolest features is that you can customize the watch face with any photo you like. My kid has become obsessed with designing unique watch faces every dayshes got a new look every time she goes to school, and she loves showing off her personalized designs to her friends. Its a fun way for her to feel special.

      The watch also lets her check texts and answer calls, which is super handy for us as parents. Its reassuring knowing we can easily get in touch with her when needed. The touchscreen size is just right for little fingers, and the text is clear. Battery life has been surprisingly goodshe can go 2-3 days on a single charge, which is actually better than my Apple Watch!

      Theres one built-in game on the watch that you cant delete, and you cant install any other games, but its not a big deal. Its a fun way for her to pass time when waiting for something. Plus, it even comes with a calculator, which has been unexpectedly useful.

      All in all, its a great watch for kids who want to feel grown-up without the price or risk of an Apple Watch. Definitely a win in my book!
